Class SpanCustomizingContainerFilter

java.lang.Object
brave.jaxrs2.SpanCustomizingContainerFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.ws.rs.container.ContainerRequestFilter
@Provider
@ConstrainedTo(SERVER)
public final class SpanCustomizingContainerFilter
extends Object
implements javax.ws.rs.container.ContainerRequestFilter
Adds application-tier data to an existing http span via ContainerParser.

Use this when you are tracing at a lower layer with brave.servlet.TracingFilter.
